	measure 'PAY002 Outside Agents' = ```
			
			    CALCULATE(
			        [PAY000 Base Payment Sum],
			        COM_CATEGORY[ComCatID] = 2
			    )
			```
		formatString: \$#,0.00;(\$#,0.00);\$#,0.00
