	measure 'TAG007 Comm Curr Month' = ```
			
			VAR _currMonth = 
			    CALCULATE(
			        MAX( 'CALENDAR'[Month_Year] ),
			        'CALENDAR'[Month_Offset] = 0
			    )
			VAR _result = "Current Month Commissions | " & _currMonth
			RETURN
			    _result
			```
		displayFolder: 99.TAGs
		lineageTag: 64a7ca20-7224-4dab-80d6-9eb7c04b55d7

